data.description: BACK ON MARKET!! Looking for a brick ranch home on James Island that you can personalize yourself less than 15 minutes to Folly Beach?  Look no further...the potential of this home is endless!  On almost a 1/4 acre, there is an eat in kitchen and comfortable living space with 3 beds and 1.5 baths.  The half bath has an option for a shower if a closet is closed in.  Original hardwood floors in many rooms and tile in bathrooms.  Large screened in back porch to enjoy your morning coffee.  Don't miss out on this amazing opportunity...Schedule your showing today!A $1,700 Lender Credit is available and will be applied towards the buyer's closing costs and pre-paids if the buyer chooses to use the seller's preferred lender. This credit is in addition to any negotiated seller concessions.
